VL53L0X support
===============

Profiles
--------
- standard:
	- signal rate limit		0.25
	- VCSEL pulse pre range	14
	- VCSEL pulse final range	10

- long range:
	- signal rate limit		0.1
	- VCSEL pulse pre range	18
	- VCSEL pulse final range	14

- normal speed/accuracy
	- timing budget			33ms
- high speed
	- timing budget			20ms
- high accuracy
	- timing budget			200ms

Accuracy measured in standard mode:
	- good from 20mm (+/-3mm) to 750mm (+/-10mm)
	- not checked withother modes

